#Window Management

Go to next / previous window 
[ Meta ] + [ k / j ]

Adjust window size 
[ Meta ] + [ h / j ] 

Move window whitin tiles 
[ Meta ] + [ Shift ] + [ j / k ]

Move window to workspace 
[ Meta ] + [ Shift ] + [ 1-9 ]

Float or Dock a window 
[ Meta ] + [ Shift ] + [ Space ]

Float and move window 
[ Meta ] + [ LClick ] + [ Drag ]

Resize floating window 
[ Meta ] + [ RClick ] + [ Drag ]

Fullscreen window 
[ Meta ] + [ f ]

Stick a winwod to all workspaces 
[ Meta ] + [ s ] 

#Workspaces

Go to workspace 
[ Meta ] + [ 1-9 ]

Show windows on all workspaces 
[ Meta ] + [ 0 ]

Go to previous workspace 
[ Meta ] + [ Tab ]

Toggle window gaps
[ Meta ] + [ a ]

Increase decrease window gaps
[ Meta ] + [ Shift ] + [ z / x ]	

#Layouts

[ Meta ] + [ t ] Tiling mode
[ Meta ] + [ T ] Bottom stack mode
[ Meta ] + [ F ] Floating mode
[ Meta ] + [ y ] Fibonacci mode
[ Meta ] + [ Y ] Reverse Fibonacci
[ Meta ] + [ u ] Master on left, cycle right
[ Meta ] + [ U ] Fullsize and cycle
[ Meta ] + [ i ] Ceter master window
[ Meta ] + [ I ] Float master window
[ Meta ] + [ o / O ] Master + / -
#Monitors

Shift window to next / previous monitor 
[ Meta ] + [ Shift ] + [ h / l ]

Shift Focus to next / previous monitor 
[ Meta ] + [ <- / -> ]

#Misc

Power actions [ Meta ] + [ backspace ]
All binaries [ Meta ] + [ d ]
Browser [ Meta ] + [ w ]
Terminal [ Meta ] + [ Enter ]
File Manager [ Meta ] + [ e ]
Lock Screen [ Meta ] + [ l ]
Screenshot [ Shift ] + [ PrtScn ]
Music Player [ Meta ] + [ m ]
Sound Control [ Meta ] + [ F4 ]
Calculator [ Meta ] + [ ' ]
